WEBVTT

00:02:27.021 --> 00:02:30.371
with any of the other
children at the orphanage,

00:02:30.395 --> 00:02:31.979
and now I know why.

00:02:32.465 --> 00:02:38.857
My adoption photos show the picture
of a frightened, malnourished little girl.

00:02:39.462 --> 00:02:43.908
Just imagine my culture shock
a short and lonely nine months later,

00:02:43.932 --> 00:02:45.481
as I arrived in America,

00:02:45.505 --> 00:02:48.243
where everything was different:

00:02:48.267 --> 00:02:49.996
the people,

00:02:50.020 --> 00:02:51.257
the buildings,

00:02:51.281 --> 00:02:52.766
the food

00:02:52.790 --> 00:02:54.116
and the clothing.

00:02:55.203 --> 00:02:57.476
As a three-year-old child,
I quickly figured out

00:02:57.500 --> 00:03:00.846
that no one spoke
the Korean language that I spoke,